{
  "texts": [
    "Software Quality AssuranceIn this subsection, we review related work on testing, vulnerability detection, bug detection, and fault localization, with a focus on how LMA systems are being employed to enhance software quality assurance processes.",
    "Fuzz4All [149] generates testing input for software systems across multiple programming languages.",
    "In this framework, a distillation agent reduces user input while a generation agent creates and mutates inputs.",
    "AXNav [123] is designed to automate accessibility testing.",
    "It interprets natural language test instructions and executes accessibility tests, such as VoiceOver, on iOS devices."
  ]
}